  <doctext>&lt;!DOCTYPE html PUBLIC &quot;-//W3C//DTD XHTML 1.0 Strict//EN&quot; &quot;http://www.w3.org/TR/xhtml1/DTD/xhtml1-strict.dtd&quot;&gt;
&lt;html xmlns=&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot; xml:lang=&quot;en&quot;&gt;
&lt;head&gt;
&lt;title&gt;E2 on Steroids Template&lt;/title&gt;
&lt;meta http-equiv=&quot;Content-type&quot; content=&quot;text/html;charset=iso-8859-1&quot; /&gt; 
&lt;!--
Obviously we won't have the style tag in the production version - this is just to get something up and running.
--&gt;
&lt;style type=&quot;text/css&quot;&gt;
body
{
text-align: center;
margin: 0 auto;
background-color: #aaa;
font-family: Arial Unicode MS, Helvetica, Sans-Serif;
font-size: 85%;
}
a, a:link
{
text-decoration: underline;
color: #66f;
}
a:visited
{
color: #a6f;
}
a:hover
{
text-decoration: none;
border: 0;
color: #f6a;
}
abbr, acronym
{
border-bottom: 1px dotted #eee;
}
kbd
{
font-family: Courier New,Mono;
border-top: 3px solid #ccc;
border-left: 3px solid #ccc;
border-bottom: 3px solid #999;
border-right: 3px solid #999;
padding: 1px 3px;
background-color: #eee;
margin: 8px 0px;
}
kbd:hover
{
border-bottom: 3px solid #ccc;
border-right: 3px solid #ccc;
border-top: 3px solid #999;
border-left: 3px solid #999;
padding: 1px 3px;
background-color: #ddd;
}
#Page
{
text-align: left;
margin: 5px auto;
width: 960px;
background-color: #fff;
}
#H
{
background-color: #ccc;
border: 1px solid #aaa;
padding: 10px;
margin-bottom: 15px;
}
#Logo
{
float: left;
width: 14%;
border: 1px solid green;
}
ul#TopNav
{
float: right;
list-style: none;
margin: 0 0 20px 0;
padding: 0;
width: 84%;
text-align: right;
}
#TopNav li
{
display: inline;
margin: 0;
padding: 0;
}
#TopNav a
{
padding: 10px;
border-top: 1px solid #aaa;
border-left: 1px solid #aaa;
border-right: 1px solid #aaa;
}
#Content
{
float: left;
width: 700px;
}

.Node
{
padding: 10px;
}

.Node .H h1,
.Node .H h2,
.Node .H h3,
.Node .H h4,
.Node .H h5,
.Node .H h6
{
margin: 0;
padding: 0 3px;
}

.Node .Node
{
border: 1px solid #ccc;
background-color: #f5f5f5;
margin-bottom: 15px;
}

.Node .Node .H
{
border-bottom: 1px dotted #666;
background-color: #aaa;
font-weight: bold;
font-size: 85%;
margin: -10px -10px 10px -10px;
}

.Node .Node .Node
{
background-color: #fff;
}

.Node .Node .Node .Node
{
background-color: #f5f5f5;
}

.Node .F
{
border-top: 1px dotted #ccc;
margin-top: 10px;
padding-top: 10px;
}

#Sidebar
{
float: right;
width: 250px;
}

.Nodelet
{
border: 1px solid #ccc;
margin-bottom: 15px;
background-color: #eee;
}

.Nodelet .H
{
font-weight: bold;
font-size: 120%;
border-bottom: 1px dotted #666;
background-color: #aaa;
margin: 0;
padding: 3px;
}

.Nodelet .B
{
font-size: 85%;
padding: 10px
}

.Nodelet .F
{
font-size: 75%;
border-top: 1px dotted #ccc;
padding: 5px 10px;
}

#F
{
clear: both;
background-color: #333;
color: #fff;
padding: 10px;
}

.Clear
{
clear: both;
font-size: 1px;
}
&lt;/style&gt;
&lt;/head&gt;

&lt;body&gt;
   &lt;div id=&quot;Page&quot;&gt;
      &lt;div id=&quot;H&quot;&gt;
         &lt;div id=&quot;Logo&quot;&gt;LOGO&lt;/div&gt;
         &lt;ul id=&quot;TopNav&quot;&gt;
            &lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;#&quot;&gt;Home&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
            &lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;#&quot;&gt;Read&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
            &lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;#&quot;&gt;Write&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
            &lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;#&quot;&gt;Chat&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
            &lt;li&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;#&quot;&gt;Personal&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
         &lt;/ul&gt;
         &lt;div class=&quot;Clear&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;
      &lt;/div&gt;

      &lt;div id=&quot;B&quot;&gt;

         &lt;div id=&quot;Content&quot;&gt;

            &lt;!--
            NOTICE that all nodes will have a class of &quot;Node&quot; (e2nodes, writeups, etc). This includes if the node is a child. The CSS can take care of styling child nodes by styling &quot;.Node .Node {}&quot;
            --&gt;
            &lt;div class=&quot;Node&quot;&gt;
               &lt;div class=&quot;H&quot;&gt;
                  &lt;h1&gt;e2node with writeup sample&lt;/h1&gt;
               &lt;/div&gt;
               &lt;div class=&quot;B&quot;&gt;
                  &lt;div class=&quot;Node&quot;&gt;
                     &lt;div class=&quot;H&quot;&gt;
                        &lt;h2&gt;([thing]) by [in10se]&lt;/h2&gt;
                     &lt;/div&gt;
                     &lt;div class=&quot;B&quot;&gt;
                        &lt;p&gt;Please ignore the CSS/styling and layout of this page. Look at the HTML instead. The basic concept is that pretty much everything has the same structure - whether it's the page, a node, or a nodelet. Each of these items has a header (H), body (B), and footer (F). If certain items are nested within another item (such as a writeup within an e2node), the child is placed in the body section of the parent.&lt;/p&gt;
                        &lt;p&gt;[in10se|I] haven't actually taken the time to code the headers and footers much yet. Suggestions are welcome. The basic skeleton is as follows&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;pre&gt;
&amp;lt;html&amp;gt;
&amp;lt;head&amp;gt;
...
&amp;lt;/head&amp;gt;
&amp;lt;body&amp;gt;
   &amp;lt;div id=&amp;quot;Page&amp;quot;&amp;gt;
      &amp;lt;div id=&amp;quot;H&amp;quot;&amp;gt;&amp;lt;/div&amp;gt;
      &amp;lt;div id=&amp;quot;B&amp;quot;&amp;gt;
         &amp;lt;div id=&amp;quot;Content&amp;quot;&amp;gt;
            &amp;lt;div class=&amp;quot;Node&amp;quot;&amp;gt;
               &amp;lt;div class=&amp;quot;H&amp;quot;&amp;gt;&amp;lt;/div&amp;gt;
               &amp;lt;div class=&amp;quot;B&amp;quot;&amp;gt;
                  &amp;lt;div class=&amp;quot;Node&amp;quot;&amp;gt;
                     &amp;lt;div class=&amp;quot;H&amp;quot;&amp;gt;&amp;lt;/div&amp;gt;
                     &amp;lt;div class=&amp;quot;B&amp;quot;&amp;gt;&amp;lt;/div&amp;gt;
                     &amp;lt;div class=&amp;quot;F&amp;quot;&amp;gt;&amp;lt;/div&amp;gt;
                  &amp;lt;/div&amp;gt;
               &amp;lt;/div&amp;gt;
               &amp;lt;div class=&amp;quot;F&amp;quot;&amp;gt;&amp;lt;/div&amp;gt;
            &amp;lt;/div&amp;gt;
         &amp;lt;div&amp;gt;
         &amp;lt;div id=&amp;quot;Sidebar&amp;quot;&amp;gt;
            &amp;lt;div class=&amp;quot;Nodelet&amp;quot;&amp;gt;
               &amp;lt;div class=&amp;quot;H&amp;quot;&amp;gt;&amp;lt;/div&amp;gt;
               &amp;lt;div class=&amp;quot;B&amp;quot;&amp;gt;&amp;lt;/div&amp;gt;
               &amp;lt;div class=&amp;quot;F&amp;quot;&amp;gt;&amp;lt;/div&amp;gt;
            &amp;lt;/div&amp;gt;
         &amp;lt;/div&amp;gt;
      &amp;lt;/div&amp;gt;
      &amp;lt;div id=&amp;quot;F&amp;quot;&amp;gt;&amp;lt;/div&amp;gt;
   &amp;lt;/div&amp;gt;
&amp;lt;/body&amp;gt;
&amp;lt;/html&amp;gt;
&lt;/pre&gt;

&lt;h1&gt;Header 1&lt;/h1&gt;
&lt;h2&gt;Header 2&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;Header 3&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;h4&gt;Header 4&lt;/h4&gt;
&lt;h5&gt;Header 5&lt;/h5&gt;
&lt;h6&gt;Header 6&lt;/h6&gt;
