   &lt;tr&gt;
      &lt;th&gt;Header Column A&lt;/th&gt;
      &lt;th&gt;Header Column B&lt;/th&gt;
   &lt;/tr&gt;
   &lt;tr&gt;
      &lt;td&gt;Row 1 Col A&lt;/td&gt;
      &lt;td&gt;Row 1 Col B&lt;/td&gt;
   &lt;/tr&gt;
   &lt;tr&gt;
      &lt;td&gt;Row 2 Col A&lt;/td&gt;
      &lt;td&gt;Row 2 Col B&lt;/td&gt;
   &lt;/tr&gt;
&lt;/table&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Paragraph with &lt;b&gt;bold&lt;/b&gt; &lt;em&gt;italics&lt;/em&gt; &lt;u&gt;underline&lt;/u&gt; &lt;abbr title=&quot;abbreviation&quot;&gt;abbrev&lt;/abbr&gt; &lt;acronym title=&quot;Duh, &amp;quot;acronym&amp;quot; isn't an acronym - get your mouse off of me&quot;&gt;acronym&lt;/acronym&gt; &lt;sup&gt;super&lt;/sup&gt;script &lt;sub&gt;sub&lt;/sub&gt;script, &lt;var&gt;variable&lt;/var&gt; and &lt;samp&gt;sample&lt;/samp&gt;. I can't remember any more inline tags to test at the moment.&lt;/p&gt;

